{"tid":1439235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"思想植入","createTime":"2019-08-10T04:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T06:18:25.000Z","uid":77666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"664a2729df4c68e4f10957198ae866f5b22ed943","tid":1439235,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"參考「乾炒牛河多冰」巴打POST <br />\n面對我地內部:<br />\n分化越黎越多<br />\n勇武開始捉左膠<br />\n左膠開始搞大台<br />\n現場既物資越黎越豐富 但引起既迴響越黎越細<br />\n每日出面大量對罵POST、飛機POST、恥笑POPO記招POST<br />\n<br />\n小弟想提出一個極重要既思考模式 &ndash; 獨立思想 (雖然成日提及 想溫故知新) <br />\n我地五大訴求好清析<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">- 徹惡法<br />\n- 銷控罪<br />\n- 查警暴<br />\n- 非暴動<br />\n- 真普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下問題必須要經常問自己 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每個行動 / POST / 思想 係咪可以幫助或促進達致五大訴求 <br />\n(呢個最重要)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n上面問題可以分拆成以下既問題<br />\n1. 呢項行動 / POST / 思想係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係乜野?</span></strong>                 - <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WHAT</span></strong><br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如何做? </span></strong>                                                         - <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HOW</span></strong><br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要做?</span></strong> 即係問 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好處與壞處 兩邊都要分析</span></strong>  -<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> WHY (極重要)</span></strong></span><br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對象係邊個?</span></strong>  預計佢地既反應係如何?            - <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WHO</span></strong><br />\n5. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時做?  </span></strong>                                                         - <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WHEN</span></strong><br />\n5. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">邊度做?  </span></strong>                                                         - <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WHERE</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無論對家點解分化 煽動我地 只要將上面6個細問題 套入每個既行動 / POST / 思想  分析下係咪可以幫助或促進達致五大訴求就可以 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>麻煩各位 對對罵、飛機、所有恥笑POST(東方、POPO記招......) 睇下就算 由得佢沉 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地既選擇正確POST回應 就係可以其中一個可以幫助或間接促進達致五大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無大台，不分化，不譴責，不割蓆，不篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"84d010c2feb15a056223a8647f2ce975ae110881","tid":1439235,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"推行動post呀<br />\n<br />\n 【置頂+廣傳】８.１０ 大 埔 逃 生 路 線 圖 （附 廣 場 名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e33ab88be7656322438b4d95451bf1f5853bcba","tid":1439235,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8f636cc30a0810e4d47545d1d86b760354906f2","tid":1439235,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:35:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cab872defc76ebc1ff2693f91fc9eb4293d1218","tid":1439235,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}